> Using OptTup

```catala-metadata
#[test]
#[testcase.testui]
#[testcase.test_description = ""]
#[testcase.test_title = "Rich"]
declaration scope Calc_rich:
  output calc scope OptTup.Calc
```

```catala
scope Calc_rich:
  definition calc.maybe_amount equals Present content $42.50
  definition calc.pair equals (7, $3.00)
  definition calc.mixed equals
    Present content (OptTup.Pair { -- first: 1 -- second: $2.00 }, OptTup.Choice.Yes content 1.5)
  definition calc.items equals [Present content 1; Absent; Present content 3]
```
